# Tech Stack - Index
Split into language-specific files (reduces AI context loading):
| File | Globs |
|------|-------|
| tech-stack-python.mdc | *.py, requirements.txt, pyproject.toml |
| tech-stack-node.mdc | *.ts, *.tsx, *.js, *.jsx, package.json |
